1. Hero Section

Large background image (nail art or salon interior)
Headline like "Your Destination for Beautiful Nails"
"Book Appointment" call-to-action button
2. Services Preview

3-4 cards highlighting top services (Manicure, Pedicure, Nail Art, Waxing, etc.)
Brief description + starting price for each
"View All Services" link
3. Gallery Preview

Grid of 4-6 best nail art photos
"See More" link to the full gallery page
4. Why Choose Us / Highlights

Walk-ins welcome
Clean & sanitized tools
Experienced technicians
Relaxing atmosphere
5. Reviews / Testimonials

2-3 Google or Facebook reviews from real customers
6. Location + Hours (quick glance)

Mini map or address with a "Get Directions" button
Today's hours prominently displayed
7. Call-to-Action Banner

"Ready for your next appointment?" with Book Now button